{"success": true, "message": "Fetched question.", "data": {"showTimer": true, "showAttemptInsight": true, "playSounds": true, "dontShowCorrectAnswerImmediately": false, "_id": "64b16a1af23ac7d519f9b15b", "classes": [], "exams": ["615d76cfc52ffa3c944600e0"], "subjects": ["615d70bd9948bc1b21da2b1f"], "chapters": ["615d6fed2b295b085ab6ebab"], "topics": [], "concepts": [], "previousYearPapers": [{"_id": "620a8a1f77301f65c2f92c4a", "title": "JEE Advanced 2012 (Paper 1)", "isVisible": true}], "position": 0, "type": "singleCorrect", "level": 2, "approximateTimeRequired": 150, "question": {"text": "The kinetic energy of an electron in the second Bohr orbit of a hydrogen atom is $\\left[a_{0}\\right.$ is Bohr radius $]$ :", "image": null}, "options": [{"id": "z86lu", "text": "$\\frac{h^{2}}{4 \\pi^{2} m a_{0}^{2}}$", "isCorrect": false, "image": null}, {"id": "iDtia", "text": "$\\frac{h^{2}}{16 \\pi^{2} m a_{0}^{2}}$", "isCorrect": false, "image": null}, {"id": "YseRt", "text": "$\\frac{h^{2}}{32 \\pi^{2} m a_{0}^{2}}$", "isCorrect": true, "image": null}, {"id": "qPjyl", "text": "$\\frac{h^{2}}{64 \\pi^{2} m a_{0}^{2}}$", "isCorrect": false, "image": null}], "correctValue": null, "solution": {"text": "As per Bohr's postulate,\r\n\r\n$\\begin{array}{l}\r\n\r\nm v r=\\frac{n h}{2 \\pi} \\quad \\text { So, } v=\\frac{n h}{2 \\pi m r} \\\\\r\n\r\n\\mathrm{KE}=\\frac{1}{2} m v^{2} \\quad \\text { So, } \\mathrm{KE}=\\frac{1}{2} m\\left(\\frac{n h}{2 \\pi m r}\\right)^{2}\r\n\r\n\\end{array}$\r\n\r\n$\\text { Since, } r=\\frac{a_{\\mathrm{o}} \\times n^{2}}{z}$\r\n\r\nSo, for $2^{\\text {nd }}$ Bohr orbit\r\n\r\n$\\begin{array}{l}\r\n\r\nr=\\frac{a_{\\mathrm{o}} \\times 2^{2}}{1}=4 a_{\\mathrm{o}} \\\\\r\n\r\n\\mathrm{KE}=\\frac{1}{2} m\\left(\\frac{2^{2} h^{2}}{4 \\pi^{2} m^{2} \\times\\left(4 a_{\\mathrm{o}}\\right)^{2}}\\right)=\\frac{h^{2}}{32 \\pi^{2} m a_{\\mathrm{o}}^{2}}\r\n\r\n\\end{array}$", "image": null}, "videoSolution": null, "numericalUpperLimit": null, "numericalLowerLimit": null, "questionLabels": [], "__v": 0, "masterId": "MOGJAPYQ68697676", "bucket": "", "category": null, "microConcepts": [], "imageBaseUrl": null, "helperText": null, "isRemoved": false, "cpyqbSubjects": ["615f0cf69476412f48314dac", "616057040283de43c87e3e16", "61bb58281213731910ea0b71", "6160579d0283de43c87e3e1f", "61964f94a5a526011886801e", "61c055f6e8ce0dc8a5c62d34", "61a8a2cce8ce0dc8a5c62d2e", "6160577e0283de43c87e3e1c", "616057210283de43c87e3e19", "629105adee9e3ae00d63352c", "62962075e7f8e9ac4daeafd8", "629f385f263330a77be9fa7e", "629f39e4ac11b26562e0625c", "61964ff3a5a5260118868022", "64d50c263df7f4a7f3017f70", "66b79b89d4b564dfab4f94d0", "678ea9a09cc79e5f592bdc12", "67fa602f4468eb1307ceb0ae", "6807d350647479b8e869647a"], "cpyqbChapters": ["61964c9ad6a0dc9c8e42ee43", "6160247352f417500b8951eb", "61e7bd7aa3ef17445bf51e09", "61bb82219193a40420bf7e41", "6160246f10291912903f0281", "61c089a5226b6f35108f63e9", "61602471c78c4e1d1f28322c", "61964c99df6eecc738334d64", "616024730f0f7fa649fe458b", "61602475757545caf939e5d2", "629f39029c652f9e50ed82eb", "629f3a885de5050309634dd5", "629109e1fe1b1ed20047dd07", "6296211a4436132dea1f813c", "64eb06c93118f713ecfef0cf", "66d5853da75f05ee8564f585", "67921d6e1d5b5072da5e9b00", "67fdff42378e1624ea7b694a", "68091fe03a10446a207fdbd5"], "cpyqbExams": ["616059150283de43c87e3e21"]}, "fetch_status": true}